.TH LEMOND "1" "November 2025" "lemond" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lemond \- Request router for Lemonade LLM serving system
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lemond
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
lemond handles request routing and load balancing for the Lemonade
LLM serving system. It distributes requests across available LLM instances
for optimal performance.
.SH OPTIONS
Run \fBlemond --help\fR for detailed usage information.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lemonade (1),
.BR lemonade-server (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Lemonade SDK developers
.SH REPORTING BUGS
Report bugs at: https://github.com/lemonade-sdk/lemonade/issues
